name: Luca Maxim - Do u Bleed At All ?

metadata.description:
This is me trying something new. 
A song about not appearing to have human emotions.
I started making a lot of videos in which I tell stories on TikTok
Including this song. A few weeks and viral videos later I'm feeding 
into the anticipation built up around this song.
What better way to do it than dropping it on Web3 first?

Putting on my Mongolian fishing boots and I'm getting to these rare fish.
iykyk

Produced, written, recorded, Mixed & Mastered by Luca Maxim
